![](images/3.jpg)
  


4. Install the hole covers carefully to prevent the posts from breaking off. 
5. Adjust the heater control unit wire. (Refer to 07-40 HEATER CONTROL UNIT WIRE ADJUSTMENT.) 
6. Connect the negative battery cable.